						               													<description>Legends of Sherwood is a card game in which players use the general deck of robbers from Robin Hood tales: Little John, Will Scarlett, Maid Marian, Robin Hood himself and many others.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Players raid wealthy merchants and knights, hunt in the forest and have a good time in taverns to earn more gold. First player who will earn 15 golden monets will be winner.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;All the robbers are different with their unique abilities. This allows players to create interesting combos. To earn monets you may:&amp;#10;&amp;bull; send robbers to Sherwood Forest or to Nottingham to raid reach mans &amp;mdash; this is risk but it give more gold (if success, of course);&amp;#10;&amp;bull; to job or to hunt for silver;&amp;#10;&amp;bull; make many others actions with less risk.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game play in several rounds, each have 4 phases:&amp;#10;1. Night. Players gain robbers cards.&amp;#10;2. Morning. In centre of the game area places Sherwood and Nottingham cards.&amp;#10;3. Day. Players play cards and apply card's abilities.&amp;#10;4. Evening. All the cards from centre of the game area are discarded.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
